      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RUNWAY BLUE (5) has been in super consistent form recently with two minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fifth (19.71) at Healesville. Form from her last run is proving strong. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. LOVE ME LUNA (2) has first look around here after a moderate run last time, finishing fifth at Healesville over 350m behind Mrs. Tiggywinkle (19.91). Worth following up. MILTON (7) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 4 lengths back in third (23.17) at this track in a Maiden over 400m. The form out of his last race has been franked. Expected to be in this for a long way. CRAFTY KID (1) is a Gary Summers-trained newcomer by Hooked On Scotch out of Missy Bale. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Can sneak into the frame at his first appearance.",
